DESCRIPTION:Indoor Play Parks are officially back! 🎉 Cozy up in the Cedar Hills Recreation Center for a variety of fun games for children under the age of six! Enjoy our mini roller coaster\, ride-on cars\, pedal cars\, mini-trampoline\, mini basketball hoops\, and other play toys! ***Before you go – check THPRD’s website  – activity calendar for facility closures throughout the season. \n\nCedar Hills Recreation Center: Tuesdays/Thursdays 10am-12pm\n$8 out of district\, $5.75 cedar hills/free for adults\n\n 
