SUMMARY:All Saints Open House
DESCRIPTION:Join us for Open House – January 15th and March 12th at 6:00 pm in the Pavilion on the All Saints campus. \n\n\nMeet our team and discover a faith-centered education that builds confident\, compassionate kids\, grades Prek – 8. \n\n\n\nGive your child the opportunity to experience a world of learning through art\, science\, music\, gifted teachers\, social events\, book clubs\, community projects\, academic excellence and weekly Mass.
