SUMMARY:Toddler Time: Learning Together
DESCRIPTION:Join us for our free Toddler Time: Learning Together parent-child classes for ages 2-4! This is a fun way to introduce preschool style learning alongside a parent/caregiver in a fun\, relaxed environment. We will play\, do crafts\, learn a little Italian together\, and make community! We hope you can join on the following Friday mornings: \n2026 Dates\nDates: \nMarch 6\, 13\, 20 (no class on 3/27) \nApril 3\, 10\, 17\, 24 \nAdditional dates to come for May and beyond! \nTime: 9:00am – 11:00am \nWhere: NW location – 1542 NW 14th Ave. \nTo register\, simply email administration@scuola.us and RSVP so we know we will have enough craft supplies! \nNote: Parents or a caregiver must remain with the child for the class. \nEditor’s note: This event is a community submission.
URL:https://pdxparent.com/event-single/toddler-time-learning-together-4/2026-03-13/
LOCATION:Scuola Italiana\, 1542 NW 14th Ave\, Portland\, OR\, 97209\, United States
CATEGORIES:Kids Calendar,Playgroup
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://pdxparent.com/wp-content/uploads/HEADING-Childrens-Programs-League-Spartan-6.png
ORGANIZER;CN="Scuola Italiana":MAILTO:info@scuola.us
END:VEVENT
